com.moneydance.modules.features.importlist.util
Class Preferences

java.lang.Object
  java.util.Observable
      com.moneydance.modules.features.importlist.util.Preferences

public final class Preferences
extends Observable

This preferences class contains the values the user can control in the application. It serves as a facade abstracting Moneydance's UserPreferences (received from the FeatureModuleContext).

Author:
Florian J. Breunig
